rganisations to collude?</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold">              </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold">20</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold">              </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold">A misplaced loyalty and power are prioritised above truth and </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold">justice</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold">.  </span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold">              </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold">21</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold">              </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold">The neglected moral values of policing.</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold">              </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold">22</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold">              </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold">Whither Reform?</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold">              </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold">23</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold">              </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold">Conclusion</span></p><p style="margin:6pt 0pt 0pt"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:6pt 0pt 0pt"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold">Abstract</span></p><p style="margin:6pt 0pt 0pt"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold">1</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">              </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">What I find is a</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">n alleged</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">conspiratorial </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">chain of </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">criminal </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">collusion where</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt"> professional and </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">inter-professional</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt"> loyalties are more important than the truth</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt"> or the rights of lay</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt"> citizens</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">.  </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">I have reason to believe this is part of a wider malaise.  I suggest a response</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">, albeit an inadequate one</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">.  </span></p><p style="margin:6pt 0pt 0pt"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold">Events</span></p><p style="margin:6pt 0pt 0pt"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold">2</span><span style="f