of the Police Authority (C</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">hair</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">), the PA Clerk and the </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">Detective Chief Superintendent</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">.  </span></p><p style="margin:6pt 0pt 0pt"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:6pt 0pt 0pt"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold">3</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">              </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold">The Chief wanted a review.  </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">The raw figures </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">went unnoticed amongst those for the big cities.  </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">However w</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">hen I calculated VAP per 1000 population (which the Home Office did not do) the anomaly stood out.  </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">Yet</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt"> a</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">newly</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt"> arrived</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt"> C</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">hief Constable</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">, </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">(CC)</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">di