; font-size:12pt">. </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">Officer Potential Whistleblowe</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">r (PWB)</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">had information to</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt"> falsify</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt"> this complaint</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">.</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">  </span></p><p style="margin:6pt 0pt 0pt"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:6pt 0pt 0pt"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold">4</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">              </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold">Bullying a potential whistleblower.  </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">Tshire’s </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">Complaints and Discipline Department</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt"> (</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">C&amp;D</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">)</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">, reporting to DCC,</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">started to investigate </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">PWB</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">,</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt"> his </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">estranged wife </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">and </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">family</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">.  </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">PWB believes t</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">hey looked at </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">his, his </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">family</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">’s</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">and his wife’s business </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">bank accounts, telephone records, utility bills, </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">community charges, </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">tapped their phones</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">, told the Inland Revenue </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">without evidence </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">they were guilty</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">of “widespread tax evasion”,</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">made 45 house to house enquiries about</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt"> their marriage; and told their son’s local education authority</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">240</span><span style="font-family:'